<dl id="n36219c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n36" href="#n36219c">N36 (VI.B.29)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n36all.htm#n36219c"> 219(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ Molomie</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Mormonism.]</font> &hellip; and the Words of Mormon begins: &ldquo;And now, I, Mormon, being about to deliver up the record which I have been making, into the hands of my son, <mark>Moroni</mark>, behold I have witnessed almost all of the destruction of my people, the Nephites.&rdquo; <small> Charles W. Ferguson, <a name="CFCT" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CFCT"><cite title="source">The Confusion of Tongues</cite></a> (1928; rpt. May 1929) 372</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
